newsletter_entries.name: Chikondi Banda
newsletter_entries.blurb: Chikondi Banda joins the Information Technology team as an IT Support Officer, bringing strong technical skills and a passion for providing efficient user support. He is focused on ensuring smooth system operations and timely assistance across the organization.

newsletter_entries.name: Thandiwe Mbewe
newsletter_entries.blurb: Thandiwe Mbewe joins the Operations team as a Customer Service Assistant, where she will support customer engagement and service delivery. She brings a positive attitude and a strong commitment to delivering excellent customer experiences.

newsletter_entries.name: James Potani
newsletter_entries.achievement: James Potani is recognized for his consistent dedication, technical expertise, and dependable support of the organizations information systems. Over the years, he has played a key role in maintaining system stability, improving IT processes, and supporting business operations through reliable and innovative solutions. His commitment and professionalism continue to make a meaningful impact across the organization.
